examples.en: I had my first ride in a limousine.
A black limousine passed by when she looked out the window.
The singer was spirited away in a limousine after the show.
We glimpsed the Queen as she got into her limousine
A chauffeur opened the door of the limousine for the grand lady.
The bride and groom rode in a limousine from the church to the reception hall.
The singer was conveyed from her hotel to the airport by limousine.
The women cackled when they saw the movie star step out of the limousine.
The limousine chauffeur was easily distinguished from the cab drivers by his livery.
After stepping out of their hired limousine, the prom couple made a theatrical entrance in their evening clothes.
